fields.title: About Xenia Concerts
fields.mainDescription:
The mission of Xenia Concerts Inc. is to offer high-quality music and arts performances, presentations, and educational programs in an environment that welcomes those who face systemic and social barriers to inclusion at typical arts events.\
\
By reimagining music and arts events and activities to make them inclusive, relevant, and accessible to all members of society, Xenia strives towards improving quality of life and promoting the enjoyment of the arts.
